	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[5.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Yes, Gornit is doable at 39. Pretty much any pet will work on him. I first killed him at level 41 with my fire pet that was buffed up with burnout 2. Start off with a malise on him and just send your pet in that is dual-wielding weapons and has burnout and a damage shield. Nuke enough times to do a good amount of damage, but stay far back and don't chain nuke, or else he will probably come after you. Back when I played my highest level magician, magician pets couldn't dual wield, and I could kill him fairly easily at 42. Since pets can duel wield now, you should be able to take him at 39 with no problems. Have fun! He drops awesome money!<br><br>Former Everquest Addict.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
